"async/go-loop" is a macro that takes a function that takes a channel as an argument and a
transducer function. It will repeatedly call the function with the channel as an argument and
process the channel with the transducer.

The transducer is a function that takes a channel as an argument and returns a channel. It will
be called with the channel that is passed to the function.

The function is a function that takes a channel as an argument. It will be
